just putting this on?

97
00:10:30,520 --> 00:10:34,844
Yes, I understand. I'm not retarded.
-No, of course not.

98
00:10:35,040 --> 00:10:38,283
The question is, what is the cause?

99
00:10:38,480 --> 00:10:41,404
Oh, I can tell you right away.

100
00:10:42,000 --> 00:10:43,923
Please sit down.

101
00:10:50,360 --> 00:10:53,807
How long is it since Abel
has been outside?

102
00:10:54,000 --> 00:10:56,731
Two years.
-Ten years.

103
