109
00:11:14,960 --> 00:11:16,689
You were there, at the birth?

110
00:11:17,360 --> 00:11:19,840
Yes, of course, yes.

111
00:11:20,040 --> 00:11:24,090
Well, I was in the corridor, but
I know exactly what happened.

112
00:11:24,440 --> 00:11:27,683
The first few weeks he had signs
of slight paralysis.

113
