What's going on?

215
00:19:58,800 --> 00:20:01,883
No hors-d'oeuvre, one fish finger,
one vegetable, no afters.

216
00:20:02,080 --> 00:20:04,811
I'm not a bloody proletarian!

217
00:21:20,240 --> 00:21:23,847
So, this is Abel then.

218
00:21:25,080 --> 00:21:27,560
You don't want to go outside?

219
